com.gridgraph.graphcore.computer.execute

Class GridComputerAdjacentVertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.structure.GridElement
      • com.gridgraph.structure.GridVertex
        • com.gridgraph.graphcore.computer.execute.GridComputerAdjacentVertex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.util.Host, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex

    public class GridComputerAdjacentVertex
extends GridVertex
    A wrapper class for GridVertex instances representing adjacent vertex of the star vertex inside graph computing environment. Specifically, operations that are valid on adjacent vertex in computing environment are implemented here.
    Author:
    guobao.chen
